This small dataset shows a sample of vehicles that seemed to me amazing,beautiful,powerfull due to their design,features and performance. They span the era of the 80s to the late 90s.¶

We try to gather the most important features and how their are related¶

Finally, we calculate their emissions and how far they are from 95 gr./por km of CO 2 dictated by the EU on 2021.¶

In [8]:
columns = df.select_dtypes(exclude="object").drop("target", axis=1).columns
fig, axs = plt.subplots(len(columns),1,figsize=(5,5*len(columns)))
for i in range(len(columns)):
    column_name = columns[i]
    sns.histplot(df, x=column_name, hue="target", multiple="stack",ax =axs[i])
